div.p:
x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n}dx=x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n}dx+nx^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-1}adx-nx^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-1}adx-n.\overline{n-1}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-2}aadx+n.\overline{n-1}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-2}aadxetc.loco
          cujus scribendum sic est
            x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n}dx=x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n}dx+\frac{n}{m+1}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-1}adx-\frac{n}{m+1}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-1}adx-\frac{n.\overline{n-1}}{\overline{m+1}^{2}}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-2}aadx+\frac{n.\overline{n-1}}{\overline{m+1}^{2}}x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n-2}aadxetc.
          nam non ex illius sed ex huius integratione provenit \int
            x^{m}\textrm{l}x^{n}dx=\frac{x^{m+1}\textrm{l}x^{n}}{m+1}-\frac{nx^{m+1}\textrm{l}x^{n-1}a}{\overline{m+1}^{2}}+\frac{n.\overline{n-1}x^{m+1}\textrm{l}x^{n-2}aa}{\overline{m+1}^{3}}\textrm{
            etc.}
